text:
Ordered red tea longan for $2.20. Their dessert priced around $1.80 to $2.80

Pro
Red tea jelly taste. One of the better tasting red tea jelly.

Longan. Well is longan can't get wrong with that.

Meh
Slightly on the too sweet side especially when not stirred well.

Ice not that well shaved. Not very snowy with bigger solid ice.

Cons
Red tea jelly not easy to cut. Should cut the jelly onto smaller pieces before serving.

Best dessert stall ever.
Have been trying their cold dessert and is marvelous.
Try out their hot dessert and is superb too.
Go support the friendly uncle and you will come back for more.
Desserts are really good and affordable, must try the fu zhok and pulut hitam! ðŸ’¯
Awesome Thai style Tapioca & friendly owners.
Ginkgo yuba is very delicious. Barley, black glutinous rice and clear soup are also good, you can try them.
